title: Country Newcomer Brett Young Is Coming To Baltimore Saturday 2/11! More Info Here! | St. Pierre | 93.1 WPOC
text:
Country Newcomer Brett Young Is Coming To Baltimore Saturday 2/11! More Info Here! posted by @stpierreonair - share 
We are psyched to tell you that newcomer Brett Young is coming to the Baltimore area!!! 
He'll be celebrating the release of his debut album (out 2/10) with a visit to Walmart on Saturday 2/11. Brett will be performing a few songs and hanging out with fans. We'd love to see you there! 
Saturday 2/11 at 6pm 
112 Carroll Island Rd 
Baltimore, MD 21220 Boston, born and raised. Big sports fan, especially the Boston teams. Running enthusiast, on a mission to complete a half-marathon in all 50 states. Any extra free time spent watching live music and catching a movie with a giant bucket of popcorn. Keep in touch! Contact
